title: DR. MARTENS X TEENAGE MUTANT NINJA TURTLES: RAPHAEL
description:
Dr. Martens have teamed up with Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles to create a 4-piece capsule collection inspired by the four characters.

The Raph boot, inspired by Raphael. He stands for being lean, mean and green.
